videoSnippet.title: Anand Should Get A Brilliancy Prize for His Game against Leko | World Rapid Championship | Round 3
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator subscribers.videos.agadmator@gmail.com

The "King Salman World Blitz & Rapid Championships 2017" in Riyadh from Decemer 26th to 30th. The first five rounds of the rapid tournament take place on December 26th. A record $2 million prize fund has attracted most of the world's best players.

Viswanathan Anand vs Peter Leko
World Rapid Championship (2017), Riyadh KSA, rd 2, Dec-26 
Italian Game: Italian Variation (C50)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. O-O Nf6 5. d3 O-O 6. h3 d6 7. c3 a6 8. a4 Ba7 9. Nbd2 Ne7 10. Re1 c6 11. Bb3 Ng6 12. Bc2 Re8 13. d4 Nh5 14. Nf1 Nhf4 15. Ng3 ed4 16. cd4 d5 17. e5 c5 18. Bg6 Ng6 19.
